main event: One clear shaped aluminum object was seen flying for 10 to 15 seconds in Alpena, Michigan on November 21, 1957.
interesting points: The object was described as a clear shaped aluminum object.
The sighting lasted for 10 to 15 seconds.
The observer was concerned that the object might have been a P-102 aircraft.
The report includes photographs of the sighting.
The sighting occurred on November 21, 1957 at 2311 hours.
